title: Episode 14: Dear Heavenly Father
itunes:title: Episode 14: Dear Heavenly Father
description:
Bobby tells Ronda to get back to the mountains like Rocky.

Khalyla threatens Gilbert with guava leaves.

We say a prayer to a sexually ambiguous God.

Khalyla just wants a hello.

 

Recorded November 16, 2015

Music by Bobby Lee
